query:
SELECT 
  sr.supplierId,
  s.companyName,
  sr.serviceType,
  sr.serviceLevel,
  sr.countryCode,
  sr.cityId,
  sr.rateUsdCents,
  sr.isServiceable
FROM supplierRates sr
INNER JOIN suppliers s ON s.id = sr.supplierId
WHERE sr.countryCode = 'AU'
  AND sr.serviceType = 'L1_NETWORK'
  AND sr.serviceLevel = 'next_business_day'
  AND sr.cityId IS NULL
  AND sr.isServiceable = 1
LIMIT 10;
